ontologie

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • ontologie.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the Event class in the ontology. An event is a child in a parent-child hierarchy. Each event has one or many attributes and inherits his parents'attributes.
    Author:
    cossin
